I have changed this because the current wording was not easy to grasp for a lay person. I think this is clearer and is also taken from the hatnote of [[global warming]] with the addition of the human influences part. Nowadays, the term climate change is much more commonly used for the man-made part so we need to point people easily to the "right" article, i.e. global warming. Eventually we should probably change the article titles!
